name: Leah's Daydream Drawing by Mouse
description:
This is my inaugural piece after joining HEN. It's called "Leah's Daydream Drawing by Mouse".
Yes, it was made fully with only Mouse and a Painter app. The result is messy but contains certain beauty. 

Leah is 7 year-old girl who wants to be everything. But she has to sit down for 9 hours a day and can only daydream.

More coming. Thanks for all supports.
